%N A349219 a(n) is the Y-coordinate of the n-th point of the 7-dragon curve; sequence A349218 gives X-coordinates.
%C A349219 Coordinates are given on a hexagonal lattice with X-axis and Y-axis as follows (the Y-axis corresponds to the sixth primitive root of unity):
%C A349219            Y
%C A349219           /
%C A349219          /
%C A349219         0 ---- X
%C A349219 The 7-dragon curve can be represented using an L-system.
