%e A349219 The 7-dragon curve starts as follows:
%e A349219          14    12
%e A349219           \   / \
%e A349219            \ /   \
%e A349219           10,13--8,11
%e A349219              \   / \
%e A349219               \ /   \
%e A349219          2---3,6,9---7
%e A349219           \   / \
%e A349219            \ /   \
%e A349219       0----1,4----5
%e A349219 - so a(0) = a(1) = a(4) = a(5) = 0,
%e A349219      a(2) = a(3) = a(6) = a(7) = a(9) = 1,
%e A349219      a(8) = a(10) = a(11) = a(13) = 2,
%e A349219      a(12) = a(14) = 3.
